info.author: Peter Bouda
info.description: FotoTagger is a metadata editor for your photos and images. With FotoTagger you may simply add a title, tags and description to your photos without the need to import the photos to a complex photo managing software. FotoTagger uses IPTC and EXIF metadata and displays a link to Google Maps if your photo contains EXIF GPS metadata.
info.name: fototagger
info.summary: Metadata editor for your photos and images
